---

<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
            <p class="text-green-dark text-sm font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Who We Are</p>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
                A Different Approach to Healthcare
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                At St Catherine's Group, we believe that exceptional healthcare starts with
                truly understanding the individual. Our approach centres on building meaningful
                relationships with every person we work with, ensuring care that is as unique
                as you are.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-green-dark flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Person-Centred</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                    Every care plan is tailored to the individual, built around your
                    specific needs, goals, and circumstances.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-green-dark flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Trusted Expertise</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                    Our team of qualified professionals brings years of experience
                    and a genuine commitment to your wellbeing.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center group">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-5 rounded-xl bg-green-dark flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Collaborative Care</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                    We work alongside you and your support network to deliver
                    care that makes a real, lasting difference.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
